5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Conway BR. (2009). Color vision, cones, and color-coding in the cortex. Neuroscientist. 15(3):274-90. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19436076\">19436076</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\nConway BR. (2001). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jneurosci.org/reprint/21/8/2768\">Spatial structure of cone inputs to color cells in alert macaque primary visual cortex (V-1).</a> J Neurosci. 21(8):2768-83. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11306629\">11306629</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2227\nCached time: 20180915124859\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.120 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.152 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 977/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 6488/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1132/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 16/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 6888/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.032/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.35 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  127.860      1 -total\n 67.20%   85.927      1 Template:Reflist\n 28.00%   35.798      1 Template:Main\n 27.84%   35.598      1 Template:Cite_journal\n 16.64%   21.281      5 Template:PMID\n 14.74%   18.842      5 Template:Catalog_look